memberdef.name: SupportedUrl_partsFromString

briefdescription.para: Functions to allow parsing a (limited) URL.

detaileddescription.para: The stack uses URLs at various points. This is a central interface to bundle parsing URLs. It is currently limited to extracting schemes, IP/host, port and the rest (path + query)
Note that none of the information is copied and thus vanishes with the original data.
